description:
A DLC pack for GROOVE COASTER WAI WAI PARTY!!!! that includes 10 songs, navigators, and avatars!

This pack includes the following content.

■Song Pack (10 songs)
・No Way Out / ARM(IOSYS)
・Stardust Vox / DJ Laugh a.k.a. uno (IOSYS)
・HB-axeleration / Tsukasa feat. Erica Masaki
・STARLIGHT TWILIGHT -GC edit- / Tatsh feat. Ayane
・Got noir forever. / E.G.G.
・Solar Storm / xi
・Warrior / Cranky
・TAKING OFF (Massive New Krew Remix) / Remixed by Massive New Krew
・VELVET (Tatsh Remix) / Remixed by Tatsh
・???(Secret)

■Navigator
・Linka (School)　*with voice(CV: Toyota Moe)
・Yu (School)　*with voice(CV: Takatsuki Miyu)

■Avatar
・LINKA(Brave, 2D)
・YUME(WhiteMage, 2D)
・SEINE(BlackMage, 2D)
・YU(Pugilist, 2D)
・RAIZEN(2D)
・KUON(2D)

*Some content will be unlocked via missions after downloading.
name: Original Pack 8 (Arcade Memorial)
